Key Match Events: The match between Namibia and Zimbabwe on 2024-10-10 was played behind closed doors at Orlando Stadium in Johannesburg due to Namibia's financial struggles.
Pre-Game Insights: Namibia requested the match to be played without spectators to limit Zimbabwean fan support, as many Zimbabweans reside in South Africa.
Others: The match was held at Orlando Stadium, the home venue of Orlando Pirates Football Club.
